name: Discover addis ababa
description: A tourism app that helps tourists to addis ababa to discover destinations This app helps tourists to discover tourism destinations across the City of Addis Ababa. The app helps tourists and travelers to addis to have the best tourism experience they would ever imagine by assisting tourists from the point of entry to the point of departure. The app also supports businesses and destinations to be easily discovered by potential customers. The Addis Ababa Arts, Culture and Tourism department uses this app to put Addis Ababa on top global tourism destinations.
